	"data": "<div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>۞يَٰٓأَيُّهَا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ لَا تَتَّبِعُواْ <a data-content='طرقه وأثاره ومذاهبه' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>خُطُوَٰتِ ٱلشَّيۡطَٰنِۚ</a> وَمَن </div><div>يَتَّبِعۡ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>خُطُوَٰتِ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٱلشَّيۡطَٰنِ فَإِنَّهُۥ يَأۡمُرُ <a data-content='ما عَظُم قبحه من الذنوب' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>بِٱلۡفَحۡشَآءِ</a> <a data-content='ما ينكره الشّرع ويكرهه الله' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>وَٱلۡمُنكَرِۚ</a> </div><div>وَلَوۡلَا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>فَضۡلُ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٱللَّهِ عَلَيۡكُمۡ وَرَحۡمَتُهُۥ <a data-content='ما تطهّر من دنس الذنوب' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>مَا زَكَىٰ</a> مِنكُم مِّنۡ أَحَدٍ أَبَدٗا </div><div>وَلَٰكِنَّ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱللَّهَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> يُزَكِّي مَن يَشَآءُۗ وَٱللَّهُ سَمِيعٌ عَلِيمٞ ١٢ <a data-content='لا يحلف أو لا يُقصّر' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>وَلَا يَأۡتَلِ</a> </div><div><a data-content='أصحاب الزيادة في الدّين' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>أُوْلُواْ ٱلۡفَضۡلِ</a></div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>مِنكُمۡ</div>