لۡخَبِيثِينَ </div><div>وَٱلۡخَبِيثُونَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>لِلۡخَبِيثَٰتِۖ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَٱلطَّيِّبَٰتُ لِلطَّيِّبِينَ وَٱلطَّيِّبُونَ </div><div>لِلطَّيِّبَٰتِۚ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> مُبَرَّءُونَ مِمَّا يَقُولُونَۖ لَهُم مَّغۡفِرَةٞ وَرِزۡقٞ كَرِيمٞ ٦٢ </div><div>يَٰٓأَيُّهَا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱلَّذِينَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ءَامَنُواْ لَا تَدۡخُلُواْ بُيُوتًا غَيۡرَ بُيُوتِكُمۡ حَتَّىٰ </div><div><a data-content='تستأذنوا ممن يملك الإذن' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>تَسۡتَأۡنِسُواْ</a></div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَتُسَلِّمُواْ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> عَلَىٰٓ أَهۡلِهَاۚ ذَٰلِكُمۡ خَيۡرٞ لَّكُمۡ لَعَلَّكُمۡ تَذَكَّرُونَ </div><div>٧٢</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'></div>",
